p: It seems to be guarding something.
A small egg lies resting in a nest.
There seems to be an old page torn from a notebook.
\b"I finally made it to the top, and to my shock my journey was well worth it. I found a new Delta Species!"
\b"It appeared to originally be a Noivern but with shiny metallic skin and flowing green grass on its neck and chest."
There seems to be an old page torn from a notebook.
\b"The two Noiverns appeared to be huddled around the eggs, and it took a while before they let me come near them. Both dragons looked really weak..."
\b"Rust had started to form on their bodies, and their yellow eyes seemed to be fading. It must've taken all of their strength to keep these eggs safe here."
\b"The one that appeared female nudged me, pushing one egg towards me. I nodded and took that egg with me, leaving the other one with the Noiverns."
\b"If you're finding these notes, please take the other egg. Keep it safe- it might be the only surviving proof that Delta Pokemon might be able to breed."
\b"And if you do find this... I will be continuing research into the breeding of Delta Pokemon."
\b"You can find me in Gaea Town. The scientist by the pond. Just mention the Noibat."
